Mercantile Stores Co Inc saidsales for the five weeks ended April four were up 0.5 pct to184.7 mln dlrs from 183.7 mln dlrs a year earlier, withsame-store sales off 1.7 pct.    Mercantile said sales for the first nine weeks of itsfiscal year were up 2.9 pct to 297.9 mln dlrs from 289.6 mlndlrs a year before, with same-store sales up 0.5 pct to 288.6mln dlrs from 287.3 mln dlrs. Reuter&#3;